<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Agriculture is one of the major industries of California and the world, and it plays a central role in human affairs. Linking knowledge of agriculture with the subject matter of the student’s major provides a useful and interesting breadth of application in areas involving economics, management, and social and environmental issues.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
